Mulberry leaf teas or extracts are used as a natural remedy for diabetes in some countries.

 Animal studies have shown some effect of mulberry leaf extract on blood glucose.

 The purpose of this trial is to assess the effect of mulberry leaf extract on type 2 diabetics, by measuring blood glucose two hours after eating a meal and taking a capsule containing either mulberry leaf extract or a placebo.

